info.name: Web Services
info.description: This is the Rest API for WebDoc Web Services. You can visit AMBISIG website in this link. To use this API, you must first generate a Hash Code. For that, you must use the Init() method which is located in the Init section of this page. This method will generate an Hash Code that must be authorized using the LoginUserBasic() method from the Login section of this page. THis Hash Code is used in every call to the API for authorization purposes. This generated Hash Code has an expiry date, when your Hash Code becomes inactive, you must create another using the steps from the line above.
